title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Sightseeing - The Netherlands - Utrecht
description:
In this video we will fly over the city Utrecht which is located in the center of the Netherlands and fly over several custom POI's being created by the community. No speech this time only some nice music so sit back and relax and enjoy this video.

The community scenario add-ons used in this video are listed below:

Utrecht - City: https://flightsim.to/file/3421/utrecht-city
Provinciehuis Utrecht: https://flightsim.to/file/3232/provinciehuis-utrecht
The Wall: https://flightsim.to/file/3143/the-wall-utrecht
Demka railroad bridge: https://flightsim.to/file/1511/demka-railroad-bridge-utrecht
Prins Claus bridge: https://flightsim.to/file/1185/prins-claus-bridge-utrecht
Rijkswaterstaat Utrecht: https://flightsim.to/file/1093/rijkswaterstaat-utrecht
Stadion Galgenwaard: https://flightsim.to/file/1031/stadion-galgenwaard-utrecht
